The LTD for Tropical Marine Research is the only and unique research laboratory for the study of tropical marine ecosystems and their services to human societies.
The mission of LTD is to provide a scientific basis for the protection and sustainable use of tropical coastal ecosystems by conducting research, capacity development and consulting activities in close cooperation with international and national partners.
